Class AmbientLight

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Styleable, EventTarget
    public class AmbientLight
extends LightBase
    Defines an ambient light source object. Ambient light is a light source that seems to come from all directions.
